.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-LOCAL-BALANCE-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-local-balance-max \- FEAT-2368 peer with highest total local_msat
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-local-balance-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the peer with the highest total local_msat summed across all their channels (FEAT-2368).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
